Go IRC Bot
----------

Acquire and build: go get github.com/StalkR/goircbot

Root directory is for "package main" and contains an example bot.
`bot` directory contains the package itself.
Plugins are available in `plugins`, inspire from them to create new plugins.
Libraries are available in `lib` for use in plugins.

Documentation: http://godoc.org/github.com/StalkR/goircbot

IRC client library: https://github.com/fluffle/goirc
Documentation: http://godoc.org/github.com/fluffle/goirc/client

Contact: goircbot@stalkr.net
